BlueGold’s Andurand Says Reports on Losses Are ‘Speculation’

-- B y   C h a n y a p o r n   C h a n j a r o e n
-- 
2011-05-11T10:41:01Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-11/bluegold-s-andurand-says-reports-on-losses-are-speculation-.html
BlueGold Capital Management LLP,
which runs a commodity hedge fund, said recent reports about its
performance this month were “speculation.”  “All numbers floating around our losses are speculation,”
Chief Investment Officer  Pierre Andurand  said today from  London ,
where the fund is based.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Chanyaporn Chanjaroen in London at 
